Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气变暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7号校舍是往这边走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有一年级新生了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,266)}在对人关系上行动选择的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现视研会有新人加入吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现视研热闹起来 高坂就更不可能改邪归正了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲 小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我一起Cosplay去招募新社员呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}绝对不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要到什么时候才肯Cosplay呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给我慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是时间的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也正聊到要不要用Cosplay来吸引新社员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 用它来代表现视研的活动 似乎太狭隘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也只有两个人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎可说是个人兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其…其实用什么方法招募都可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用…用那个来招募社员 似乎太…太强烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的气氛就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我只要有机会就不想错过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要一谈到Cosplay 个性就会大变耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找来什么怪人 我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这点早就不用当心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为早就全是些怪人了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不照惯例办那个第几回的什么会议吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然扯到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.96,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会以外的人士禁止进入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作进入第二部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为新角色登场 使得剧情有了重大的转变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家也看得津津有味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现…现在看到亚力士 还真…真让人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这在大总集篇中 可是珍贵的新作画面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且演得很热血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们能一再重复的看那么多遍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会问这种最基本的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说有趣还是无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是有趣才会看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.38,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无趣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.45,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长毕业了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开学校了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这么说来 他怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出社会工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是升上研究所？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是留级？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他到底是几年级的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着吓成那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一般人都会被吓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是做了什么亏心事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说件能让你放心的事好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此我要宣布一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算辞去会长的职位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,……这还真是突如其来的重大宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也差不多该毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“差不多”是念了几年啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这表示他到现在都没打算过要毕业吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我打算花一整年时间来专心写毕业论文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料也都收集齐全了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么资料？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算推荐斑目担任下一任会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个提议不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且实际上 你几乎就等于是会长了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且 其他四年级的就只剩原口一个人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也老是把社团的实际营运交给田中做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是先去问问田中比较好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就接下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是第二任会长 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二任？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才第二任？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且人不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}(因为种种因素 请勿摄影)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 通过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有两个新人要加入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说只是暂时加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还没见过他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会有人想加入那种社团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他们会是怎样的人 真让人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算要玩的新人大考验泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该先做个自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫泽崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝姓朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我朽朽～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会这么叫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦死了 还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部 你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让OTAKU知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 她是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她不会玩Cosplay了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是大野…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她的Cosplay迷惑了是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没“那回素”啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部 不可以做出太过激的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可是新人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 奉劝你们还是别来这个社团为好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这个房间会出现那种东西哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前去世的初代会长的鬼魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着啦 初代会长还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要随便诅咒人家死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有骗你们喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我一直都没提
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有时候会看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是书架上的这种缝隙里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有张戴着眼镜 长得像狗一样的脸浮在半空中…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么说得好像跟真的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在别回头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的书架的阴影处有一张人脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(注：此影像为想像画面)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲 你演得真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我当初料想的一样 春日部开始在整新人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要想办法阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以会长的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现代视觉文化研究会迎新餐会现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝酒是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不用勉强…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想 大家不一口气干掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真没精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说我们有我们的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春季蔬菜披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手工蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松软男爵可乐饼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笼包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸起司馄钝 然后还要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫个组合套餐如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是迎新餐会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就炸鸡块跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不吃鸡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对炸鸡块！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就取…取消炸鸡块
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换成…腌漬整…整条茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想看看中野的男子汉气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那件衣服的牌子是CECLL McBEE吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.37,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CECLL McBEE：日本知名服装品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“果然”是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很少有人可以穿出味道来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是熟人就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果第一次见面的男人就称赞自己的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会认为他另有企图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有那个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里只是为了盯住高坂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来完全不像是那样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然是像哪样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看起来只像是普通朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 触及到敏感话题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先说清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这是迎新餐会 但我可一点都不欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么说嘛 大家好好玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来想喝什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该选哪个就照神的旨意吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}两个人的Heart Balance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找点话题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}不平衡抽签
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你才是会…会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}无论是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}梦想还是憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽…朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会选择我们社团？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为大野吧 大野的Cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了不说这个的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这个之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有其它理由呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我还年幼时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对动漫画抱持着浓厚深远的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来想喝什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}在我国中跟高中时代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁调酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}由于经济因素及顾虑社会目光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}一直无法参加正式的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…学术研究活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打算利用进大学的机会 彻底改头换面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是春季蔬菜披萨以及松软男爵可乐饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人家的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自己独占
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好delicious哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想在大学改变个性是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝酒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒对我来说就像水一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在高中时就常喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不喜欢像漫研或动研那种OTAKU气息很浓的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也都是OTAKU啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这里有女生社员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光这点就完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也有到漫研去看过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全待不下去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是些想叫他去死的丑胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画现在已经是日本的文化了不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光只会享受末免也太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该要把它当成文化来研究…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的“文化”的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…次文化(subculture)吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 次文化 简称“次文”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的剧场版动画能到坎城影展参展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.56,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法国坎城影展，每年5月举行，国际所公认的一级影展之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色模型还被当成艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在苏富比拍卖会上竞标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂得还真多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些只能算是常识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁调酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁调酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁调酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这杯我来喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁调酒 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芋烧酒双份加冰块
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我也要烧酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近很流行喝烧酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的烧酒甚至比日本酒还要美味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然这副德行 但对流行可是很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天一起去喝好喝的烧酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会先把店找好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚餐吗？真是难得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是迎新餐会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几个人加入？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个 不过只是暂时加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少啊 现视研撑得下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫研虽然订了包厢 但还是挤得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都闹得可疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当上会长了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不知不觉就变成我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算来找我 我也会因为太忙而回绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 好歹也该问我一声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算是现视研的监护人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到麻烦就跟我说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲 你要不要也喝一口？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是酒桶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自己是OTAKU而自暴自弃的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得这种人是最让人看不下去的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家并没有自暴自…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪他去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是高坂去？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笹陪他去不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲 请喝一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说我不喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野 你会不会喝太多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在为我担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜欢小咲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟你一起喝酒真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你在喝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也一起喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜欢喝烧酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我可以陪你喝啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜欢小咲喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西别忘了拿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}两个人的Heart Balance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}不平衡抽签
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}无论是恋爱 梦想还是憧憬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 要不要我去帮你倒杯水？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好得很 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲 喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…我有在喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多喝一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽朽 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店最后点餐的时间就要过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问还要点些什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲 你真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我在喝了…不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很乐意为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中 要…要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽崎 你的脸色发青哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}两个人的Heart Ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家要去便便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 你的脸色还是不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？就此解散吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去续摊嘛 续摊好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想继续跟大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是每家店都打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要来我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己随便找地方坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}高…高坂 漫画借我看好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你这个新人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是别人的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 反正都是同一个社团的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是暂时加入的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺喜欢这里的 要我正式加入也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑目呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要喝可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来进行测试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入社测试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果玩那个叫什么格斗游戏的 你能够打赢高坂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你加入如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也蛮喜欢玩格斗游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要来玩看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝你还是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩吧 玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便培养感情 我会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着手下留情 照你平常的打法就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟上次玩“噗呦噗呦!”那时一样的水准喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Guilty Gear Isuka」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.00,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Guilty Gear Isuka」：罪恶装备Isuka
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个才刚出的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是常去玩大型机台的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越爱耍酷的家伙功力越弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我好好教训教训你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔起来然后直接在空中连续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂 你是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的强制取消被他给识破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然从DUST发动D Loop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂赢了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个游戏只有一回战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再比一场？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 他赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是打游戏 不过男友赢了还是很高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的程度还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两场都彻底输给了你 你居然还这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 因为你喝了酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全没喝半滴酒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却灌了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会这么强也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再打一场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去帮他打气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部 这么多人在看耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一场也赢的话 我就亲你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛从刚才起就一直大吼大叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然会叫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要亲…亲他 与测试无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有那么回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能打赢高坂 就算是新人我也亲你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一堂课在哪里上？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得他好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得你是否还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂都不会不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想说 只要每年都让高坂进行测试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以让现视研关门大吉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.04,0:24:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原 你对妹妹型的没兴趣对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.94,0:24:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较喜欢的应该是青梅竹马型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.41,0:24:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女仆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.08,0:24:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.85,0:24:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 虽然现在说这个有点老套
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.62,0:24:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 猫耳可是基本配备
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.52,0:24:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较喜欢绷带少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.29,0:24:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人前人后是两种个性的班长类型呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:24:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.36,0:24:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有角色扮演游戏或动画里面有那种角色的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹马的猫耳女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.26,0:25:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校是班长 平时态度严肃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.80,0:25:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做事常常很迷糊 浑身缠满绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.43,0:25:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在的时候完全不理男主角 没人在的时候则紧缠着不放
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好萌啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.18,0:25:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,266)}量产型制造过程的比较研究

